  <summary date="2018-02-15T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Reserve Component Benefits Parity Act of 2018

This bill makes reserve component members who are deployed to support pre-planned operations of a combatant command eligible for: (1) non-reduction in pay while serving in the uniformed services or National Guard, (2) consideration of active duty service to reduce the age for retired pay; and (3) the high-deployment allowance for lengthy or numerous deployments and frequent mobilizations.</summary>
